OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fcloudy and breezy over the Western
OL,7,FIsles and Skye with showers at times.
OL,8,FElsewhere will be dry and cold with
OL,9,Flargely clear skies leading to a frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FAfter a cold start for many
OL,12,Fit will be a dry day with some long
OL,13,Fspells of sunshine. Turning cloudier
OL,14,Fin the evening with rain spreading
OL,15,Feastwards. Breezy in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
